Uses of MobileBean in org.openmobster.cloud.api.sync
 

Subinterfaces of MobileBean in org.openmobster.cloud.api.sync
 interface MobileBeanStreamable
          This is used by server side Mobile Beans that have data like big attachments, big music files etc that are designed to not sent all the data on the first sync This data from the Mobile Bean is loaded on-demand at a later time when it needs to be used
